Arts Community Reading Initiative.

00:02:30.390 --> 00:02:33.110
Communities across this country
from Los Angeles to Wichita,

00:02:33.110 --> 00:02:35.920
Kansas to Trenton, New Jersey
have read his book as a part

00:02:35.920 --> 00:02:39.730
