Luis at their Big Read events.

00:02:45.330 --> 00:02:47.810
Big Read participants,
especially youth participants,

00:02:47.810 --> 00:02:50.000
enjoy meeting and connecting
with him.

00:02:50.000 --> 00:02:51.650
And this is no surprise to us.

00:02:51.650 --> 00:02:53.490
He is not only a really
talented writer

00:02:53.490 --> 00:02:57.290
but he is a gracious individual
and a very phenomenal speaker.

00:02:57.290 --> 00:02:59.840
It is a huge privilege to
have him here with us today.

00:02:59.840 --> 00:03:02.510
Please join me in welcoming
Luis to the stage.

