00:41:06.210 --> 00:41:09.240
She's Nigerian.

00:41:09.240 --> 00:41:13.370
And she came to our
school to write a memoir.

00:41:13.370 --> 00:41:16.420
And over the couple of
years she started to realize

00:41:16.420 --> 00:41:20.690 position:56%
