fiction and speculative fiction come

00:41:20.690 --> 00:41:23.280
out of African [inaudible].

00:41:23.280 --> 00:41:26.460
And she decided to
write science fiction

00:41:26.460 --> 00:41:30.200
with Nigerian folklore in it.

00:41:30.200 --> 00:41:33.330
